  "title": "Temp Healthiersg Ambassador - Healthcare #HZO",
  "description": "<p>Duration: 1 year contract <br />Location: West<br />Working Hours: Mon - Fri 8am - 430pm <br />Salary: $12/hour</p><p><strong>Job Scope: </strong></p><p>•\tManage the one-stop Healthier SG booth and provide assistance to patients for Healthier SG</p><p>•\tAssist with HSG assisted enrolment through small group sharing and one-to-one engagement with patients/residents in outreach settings such as hospitals, designated booths or community settings, via the mobile app or system application.</p><p>•\tExplain to patients the benefits of HSG initiatives and the importance to enrol, make the first visit to review Health Plan with the Primary Care Provider, fulfil the preventive health recommendations and follow up for review annually.</p><p>•\tAttend to HSG related enquiries from patients and caregivers.</p><p><strong>Job Requirements: </strong><br />•\tMin. A level/ Diploma in any field <br /></p><p>For interested applicants, please send your updated resume to: melissa@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>All candidates’ information will be treated with the strictest confidence</p><p>Melissa Zhang Zhiqi (Mezzo)</p><p>R2197564</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>99C4599</p>",
